  "comment": "Решение:\n\\(x(x+1)^2=2(x+1)\\)\n\\(x(x+1)^2-2(x+1)=0\\)\n\\((x+1)(x(x+1)-2)=0\\)\n\\((x+1)(x^2+x-2)=0\\)\n\\(x=-1\\) или \\(x^2+x-2=0 (2)\\)\n\\( (2) x^2+x-2=0\\)\n\\(D=1+8=9\\)\n\\(x_1=1\\)\n\\(x_2=-2\\)\nОтвет: \\(-2; -1; 1\\)",
